casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-1587. J.A. Croson Co. v. Ohio Dept. of Adm. Serv., Div. of Pub. Works.

Franklin County, No. 94APE09-1406. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective October 10, 1995.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
